{"type":null,"faqId":44086,"title":"为什么手机外放音乐最小音量时有杂音或电流音？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 喇叭属于大功率器件，通常需要功放来驱动，当音量减至最小音量时功放还是在工作，仍然会输出一定的底噪（如家庭影院在无声时也存在此类杂音），所以当耳机贴近喇叭时就能听见这个噪声；此为喇叭通路上固有的底噪，非问题，请您放心使用；另外请您在使用外放时不要将耳朵贴近喇叭，以免损伤人耳。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 在处理喇叭的外放音效上，我司使用了第三方音效调试算法；在音量减为零时，算法滤波器的误差会经由喇叭输出，即\"电流音\"，并非器件问题。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9586","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400087000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"外放,音乐,杂音,电流音,解锁,锁屏,触摸,打开软件","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}